					<div>
						<ul class="special_offers">
							<li style="LIST-STYLE-TYPE: none">
								<br>
								<span style="FONT: bold 14px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; COLOR: #5d6064">Connections Hotels Make the Gold List</span>
								<br>
								Nine hotels from Connections itineraries were recently selected for the <em>Condé Nast Traveler's</em>
								Gold List of “The World’s Best Places to Stay,” including the Esplanade Zagreb Hotel in Croatia, the Fairmont Chateau Lake Louise in Canada and the Oberoi Amarvilas in India. Proof that, on Connections journeys, luxury and authenticity go hand in hand.
							</li>
						</ul>
